title: Dremel 709-02 110-Piece All-Purpose Rotary Accessory Kit
feature: Comes with reuseable storage case and 110 accessories
Can stand upright or hang on a wall by hook
Ideal for cutting, sanding, polishing, grinding, and cleaning
Clear lid, 8 storage bins and removable trays make accessories easy to locate
A complete start-up kit for new Dremel rotary tool users
description: This 110-piece accessory kit provides the organized storage of popular Dremel accessories to perform a wide range of applications. This accessory set offers reusable storage bins and lift-out trays for easy organization of the included bits for cutting, grinding, polishing, sanding, cleaning and more. The kit consists of regular and heavy-duty cut off wheels, sanding bands, sandpaper discs, polishing compound, felt polishing wheels, aluminum oxide grinding stones, silicon carbide grinding stones, dressing stone, mandrels, wrench, and a reusable carrying case with clear lid.
